-- `Buffer' of CO2 Permits May Weigh on Market, European Union's Delbeke Says
-- B y   E w a   K r u k o w s k a   a n d   M a t t   C a r r
-- 2010-10-19T08:44:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-19/-buffer-of-co2-permits-may-weigh-on-market-european-union-s-delbeke-says.html
A “significant buffer” of carbon
permits in the European Union emissions market may depress prices
through the next decade, said Jos Delbeke, director general for 
climate at the European Commission.  The EU could opt to curb the drag by auctioning fewer
allowances, he told a Platts seminar in Brussels today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ewa Krukowska in Warsaw at 
